(This script I provided is for better understanding of Json UI. You actullay have to create new ones.)


And you'll use these websites for Json UI resources, https://wiki.bedrock.dev/json-ui/json-ui-intro.html. and https://wiki.bedrock.dev/json-ui/json-ui-documentation.html (These are for understanding.)

